                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-819898759" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="819898759">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/candyandclouds/">琴 酒</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-06-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">“汝辈非糖人，何怕日。非纸人，何怕风。非泥人，何怕雨。怕这怕那，何时能立。”</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

